🔥 IMPORTANT CONCEPTS
Concept	Meaning
PaaS	Platform as a Service
Flask	Python web framework
Render	cloud deployment platform
Procfile	app startup configuration
⚠️ COMMON ERRORS + FIXES
Error	Cause	Fix
Build failed	wrong requirements.txt	keep only Flask
Invalid username/password	GitHub password removed	use PAT token
App crashed	wrong Procfile	check startup command
Blank page	Flask app not running	verify code
